@startuml BPMN-001
!pragma layout smetana
title BPMN-001 v1.5 — Core analysis flow (BPMN-aligned activity rendering)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

|User|
start
:Choose audience, role and scenario;
if (Interaction mode?) then (Criteria-first)
  :Set criteria;
  |Workspace|
  :Generate bounded candidates;
  |User|
  :Select or compare candidates;
else (Map-first)
  :Select point, object or AOI;
endif

|Workspace|
:Build deterministic context and scores;
:Load validation governance;
|Analysis API|
:Validate request contract;
if (OpenAI result valid?) then (yes)
  :Return structured narrative;
else (no / unavailable)
  :Return deterministic fallback narrative;
endif
|Workspace|
:Merge narrative and decision score;
:Render dashboard;
fork
  :Persist analysis through repository adapter;
fork again
  :Keep recoverable in-memory UI state;
end fork
|User|
if (Export requested?) then (yes)
  |Report API|
  :Create/read report package and print route;
  |User|
  :Print or save bounded report;
endif
stop

legend bottom
  This is an implementation-aligned activity rendering, not executable BPMN XML.
  Official/client validation remains outside this automated flow.
endlegend
@enduml
